      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <span class="text-[#c5a059] text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-1 font-bold">Reservation</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold">상담 예약 신청</h2>
      </div>

